item.title: The Observer
item.author: jsacosta1103@gmail.com (Jerad Acosta)
item.description: Comfy in my cloth dress I explore this realm Looked after, maintained Through my observation Close your eyes, terminals Screens on tables, aligned Surface glow from metric input Is this where I go? Gradient, measured, intent Absent ordered direction, I Find safety glass separates us, along A body, the horizon between all absorbed, and All not
